{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"The Dragon Prince: Animasi Netflix Buatan Penulis Avatar","content":"<p>Netflix memang sudah menjadi tempat yang baik untuk serial film animasi, beberapa judul seperti  <em>Voltron: Legendary Defender, </em>dan <em>Trollhunters,</em> sukses mencuri perhatian, dan sekarang muncul pengumuman baru bahwa Netflix akan menghadirkan seri animasi terbaru berjudul <em>The Dragon Prince.</em></p>\n<p>Yang membuat <em>The Dragon Prince</em> sangat menarik ialah, film ini akan ditulis oleh Aaron Ehasz. Aaron sendiri merupakan sosok di balik suksesnya serial animasi <em>Avatar: The Last Airbender.</em></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49946\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49946\" data-attachment-id=\"49946\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/attachment/01-the-dragon-prince/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"01-the-dragon-prince\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49946 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" alt=\"avatar the last airbender\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/01-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49946\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Tiny Mixtapes</p></div></p>\n<p>Selain itu nama Justin Richmond juga terlibat dalam pembuatan film ini sebagai sutradara. Justin sebelumnya pernah menyutradarai <em>video game</em> untuk <em>Playstation 3</em> dibawah naungan Naughty Dog bersama Amy Henning. <em>Video game</em> yang dimaksud tidak lain adalah <em>Uncharted 3: Drake’s Deception</em>, <em>video game</em> pemenang <em>best visual art</em> di tahun 2011 dan <em>best PS3 game</em> tahun 2012.</p>\n<p>Dengan beredarnya beritanya ini, maka beredar juga poster <em>The Dragon Prince</em> yang memperlihatkan tiga karakter sedang berdiri di atas gundukan tanah menghadap kearah naga besar. Berikut poster sementara yang bisa dilihat:</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49947\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49947\" data-attachment-id=\"49947\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/attachment/02-the-dragon-prince/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"02-the-dragon-prince\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49947 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" alt=\"the dragon prince poster\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/02-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49947\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: IGN</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk garis besar cerita, <em>The Dragon Prince</em> akan berkisah tentang dua pangeran manusia yang menjalin ikatan kuat namun terancam akan dibunuh oleh pembunuh peri. Dari situlah akhirnya pemcarian epik untuk membawa perdamaian ke lahan perang mereka dimulai.</p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/7HWcff0YEPM\" width=\"1280\" height=\"480\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<h2>The Dragon Prince Tampilkan Cerita dan Visual Menawan</h2>\n<p>Sekilah garis besar cerita masih tentang perang dan perdamaian, hampir mirip dengan <em>Avatar: The Last Airbender.</em> Mungkin ini karena ceritanya ditulis oleh Aaron, oleh sebab itu kisahnya masih berputar di hal yang hampir sama, namun bukan berarti ini akan sangat mirip dengan Avatar, sebab kepiawaian Aaron dalam meramu cerita sudah tak bisa diragukan lagi, lagi pula kombinasi penyutradaraan Justin juga akan memberikan tampilan sudut pandang gambar yang bagus seperti <em>Uncharted 3: Drake’s Deception</em>.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49948\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49948\" data-attachment-id=\"49948\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/attachment/03-the-dragon-prince/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"03-the-dragon-prince\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49948 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" alt=\"uncharted 3\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/03-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49948\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Uncharted</p></div></p>\n<p>Untuk detil pengisi suara dan tanggal perilisan masih belum diumumkan, kemungkinan besar semua detil itu akan dijelaskan pada acara Comic-Con International di San Diego pada 21 Juli nanti oleh Aaron, Justin, dan produser eksekutif, Giancarlo Volpe.</p>\n<p>Dari semua aspek yang dimiliki oleh <em>The Dragon Prince</em>, jelas serial animasi satu ini sangat sayang untuk dilewatkan, jaminan cerita yang bagus, penyutradaraan yang piawai menjadi tolak ukur yang sangat fantastis.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49949\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49949\" data-attachment-id=\"49949\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/attachment/04-the-dragon-prince/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"04-the-dragon-prince\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49949 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" alt=\"the dragon prince aaron ehasz justin richmond\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/04-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49949\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aaron Ehasz dan Justin Richmond. Sumber: Polygon</p></div></p>\n<p>Lagi pula Netflix memang sedang “bersemangat” membuat konten menarik untuk film animasi, bahkan saat ini Netflix sedang mengerjakan serial lanjutan dari <em>Voltron: Legendary Defender,</em> selain itu Netflix juga sedang mempersiapkan sebuah film animasi adaptasi dari seri <em>video game</em> ternama; <em>Castlevania</em> yang memasuki musim kedua.</p>\n<p>Nama LeSean Thomas yang pernah terlibat dalam film <em>Avatar: Legend of Korra</em> juga dikabarkan akan mengerjakan film animasi adaptasi dari komik Cannon Busters bersama Netflix.</p>\n<p><strong>Baca Juga: <a href=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/netflix-akan-buat-kartun-fast-furious/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Netflix Akan Buat Kartun Fast &amp; Furious?</a></strong></p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_49950\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-49950\" data-attachment-id=\"49950\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/the-dragon-prince-animasi-netflix/attachment/05-the-dragon-prince/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"05-the-dragon-prince\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" class=\"wp-image-49950 size-full\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince.jpg\" alt=\"voltron netflix\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/08/05-the-dragon-prince-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-49950\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Another Drop of Ink</p></div></p>\n<p>Bagaimana apakah kalian penasaran dengan serial animasi terbaru, <em>The Dragon Prince</em> ini? Apakah kalian senang dengan usaha Netflix dalam menghadirkan serial animasi berkualitas yang bakal semakin banyak mereka garap? Jangan lupa untuk menuliskan tanggapan kalian di kolom komentar ya!</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"0cae88cb-0ce5-54ae-bbc0-160bd72b009f"}}}